Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.76,0:00:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當月光照射黑暗的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.57,0:00:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳說在宇宙飛舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.30,0:00:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,展開決鬥之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.44,0:00:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死亡的呼聲遠遠的傳開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.02,0:00:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.96,0:00:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪惡為此而戴上了面具\N希望能以此錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.80,0:00:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換取持續戮力不停\N所追求的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.87,0:00:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為命運而不知所措之\N嘆息的玫瑰念珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.24,0:00:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因無法抹去的記憶\N而為愛顫抖著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.35,0:01:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當月光照亮黑夜之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.19,0:01:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳說促使得宇宙舞動著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.16,0:01:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虛幻的墜天使們啊\N美麗的飛翔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.23,0:01:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在禁忌的決鬥展開時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.97,0:01:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死神正自遙遠的地方呼喊著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.49,0:01:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第四話塔中的小公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.66,0:01:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欸...問妳唷、問妳唷，愛娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.97,0:01:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次來到城堡的英司少爺\N他如何啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.47,0:01:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是不是還是一樣很困惑啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.17,0:01:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，不過我覺得他很努力呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.78,0:01:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了找他姊姊才來的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.95,0:01:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓人覺得好感動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.01,0:02:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我的母性本能油然而生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.98,0:02:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，他老愛鎌東鎌西的\N有夠難伺候耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.06,0:02:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布麗姬妲，不可以這樣子\N說妳負責的服務對象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.83,0:02:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是~這是事實啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.80,0:02:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛哦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.67,0:02:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受到懲罰了吧，布麗姬妲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.71,0:02:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來斗牙少爺跟英司少爺\N一樣都是17歲耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.31,0:02:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過完全不同型的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.34,0:02:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺從小就沒有出過城外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.68,0:02:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個"純粹培養"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.55,0:02:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裘伊露，晚上要小聲一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.89,0:02:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺跟英司少爺\N愛娜妳喜歡哪一個?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.96,0:02:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.09,0:02:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜腦子裡\N只有斗牙少爺一個人嘛~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.26,0:02:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事，人家...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.70,0:02:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.44,0:02:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?雪希露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.44,0:02:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.74,0:03:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.55,0:03:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.95,0:03:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該...不是其他女僕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.26,0:03:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇啊~~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.58,0:03:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安全帶檢查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.44,0:03:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血壓腦波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.25,0:03:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,測定裝置檢查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.61,0:03:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就位，OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.88,0:03:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G電位、身體提升裝置啟動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.50,0:04:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.30,0:04:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,溫柔點，再溫柔點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.51,0:04:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話， 就不叫做訓練了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.24,0:04:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香也做過這種事情嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.85,0:04:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爺，沒問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.75,0:04:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷文好像真的要磨練他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.72,0:04:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂...我跟你有仇啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.69,0:04:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然你要駕駛神機超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.40,0:04:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少得要輕鬆完成\N這種程度的訓練才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.07,0:04:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK，斗牙\N結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.34,0:04:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你，琉菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.68,0:04:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是一次不錯的訓練呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.38,0:04:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎，太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.75,0:04:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺，辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.98,0:04:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊斗牙，又創新紀錄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.79,0:04:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問你喔、問你喔，斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.99,0:04:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼樣才能做到這麼好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.89,0:04:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我一點訣竅吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.09,0:04:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,訣竅?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.03,0:04:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.10,0:05:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒做什麼特別的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.03,0:05:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，讓我再試一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.47,0:05:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不稍微休息一下是辦不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.07,0:05:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說做就做!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.84,0:05:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也好，進去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.01,0:05:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司真是可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.98,0:05:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會那麼直腸子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.12,0:05:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司幹嘛生氣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.39,0:05:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用在意沒關係的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.69,0:05:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過他還真是個頑固的孩子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.16,0:05:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.23,0:05:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，昨晚要回寢室的途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.36,0:05:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有個白影突然飄過眼前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.27,0:05:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追過去一看\N卻根本沒半個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.17,0:05:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道不會是窗簾嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.81,0:05:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們絕對沒有看錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.17,0:05:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蝶雪拉跟裘伊露\N還有瑪莉妮雅也都看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.28,0:05:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反而更難以置信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.88,0:05:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這座城堡裡會出現幽靈\N的確也沒什麼好奇怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.75,0:05:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭，別說得這麼可怕嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.59,0:06:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈比外星異種強嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.96,0:06:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你啊\N就是因為從小就接受戰鬥訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.10,0:06:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就變成\N四肢發達頭腦簡單了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.73,0:06:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多學一點常識嘛，常識!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.27,0:06:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,輪不到你來說!\N好痛哦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.50,0:06:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耳朵...\N耳朵?耳朵怎樣了?...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.38,0:06:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.58,0:06:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，搞不好那個像幽靈般\N的影子就是綾香本人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.88,0:06:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正又沒到西塔的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.15,0:06:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向女僕們打聽\N也沒有人知道綾香的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.76,0:06:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手上又只有這一點點情報而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.73,0:06:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，為什麼會找我一起呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.90,0:06:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.93,0:06:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人的話\N搞不好又會迷路的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.44,0:06:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.57,0:06:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我，綾香是個怎麼樣的人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.71,0:06:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有兄弟姊妹和家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.35,0:07:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不知道有個姊姊\N會是什麼滋味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.82,0:07:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們很要好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.02,0:07:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.29,0:07:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小時候我父母就死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.40,0:07:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後來我們姊弟就相依為命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.20,0:07:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她很溫柔、又漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.77,0:07:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腦筋雖好卻有點遲鈍\N而且又愛哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.24,0:07:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本應該只是個普通上班女郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.77,0:07:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然卻換了工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.41,0:07:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我聯絡說要到\N什麼城裡去工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.98,0:07:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以短時間內不會回家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.41,0:07:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在我開始擔心的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.78,0:07:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然收到一封她寄來的求救信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.22,0:07:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察又靠不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.59,0:07:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到處打聽之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.36,0:07:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才終於來到這座城堡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.66,0:07:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽..幽靈?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.24,0:07:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.91,0:08:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是雪貂嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.18,0:08:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會在這種地方...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.42,0:08:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，等等我一下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.62,0:08:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是通到哪兒去啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.39,0:08:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡好像是南塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.46,0:08:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,南塔?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.29,0:08:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經聽愛娜提過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.90,0:09:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這座城堡有東、西、\N南、北、及中央五座城塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.40,0:09:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒有桑德曼的允許\N絕對不可以進入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.31,0:09:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在女僕間好像也流傳著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.11,0:09:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「每一個塔都藏有著\N各自的秘密」這樣的流言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.32,0:09:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五座塔以及五個秘密啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.92,0:09:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來，綾香也是失蹤於西塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.42,0:09:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.77,0:09:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅羅多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.15,0:09:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是綾香嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.29,0:09:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不、不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.89,0:09:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳...是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.53,0:09:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說...你是女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.66,0:10:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一看就知道了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.36,0:10:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼會在這裡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.50,0:10:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.24,0:10:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳叫什麼名字?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.30,0:10:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會說話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.77,0:10:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好的回答我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.68,0:10:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊...對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.54,0:10:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.68,0:10:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.11,0:10:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司雖然動不動就生氣\N不過他是個很體貼的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒在生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.39,0:10:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看吧，又生氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.56,0:10:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是斗牙，妳是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.23,0:10:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.66,0:10:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.00,0:10:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牠呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.83,0:10:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.20,0:10:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牠見到妳好像很高興呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.30,0:10:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為它迷路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.97,0:10:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迷路?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.97,0:10:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在找牠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.41,0:10:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.58,0:10:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊...是為了找牠\N所以才半夜出來到處跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.52,0:10:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.25,0:10:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.50,0:11:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.43,0:11:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙，怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.23,0:11:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.37,0:11:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.40,0:11:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們會被罵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.15,0:11:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事情嗎，叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.88,0:11:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這麼晚了\N妳的燈還亮著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.05,0:11:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以過來看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.25,0:11:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡不著嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.89,0:11:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.76,0:11:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過羅羅多已經回來了\N所以就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.00,0:11:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.53,0:11:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N讓你做了這麼不情願的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.47,0:11:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有其他G因子擁有者的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.27,0:11:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也就不用去駕駛G戰影了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.98,0:11:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.48,0:12:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.69,0:12:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出擊了!莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.33,0:12:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅羅多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.97,0:12:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次你要乖乖的留在家裡哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.45,0:12:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂你聽到了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.92,0:12:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.92,0:12:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫做莉露的女孩\N就是駕駛G戰影的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.02,0:12:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再表示的吃驚一點嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.56,0:12:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.39,0:12:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管了，要出擊了，快走!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.26,0:12:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.34,0:13:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G戰影出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.19,0:13:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EFA已經開始戰鬥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.20,0:13:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居民的避難措施\N似乎已經完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.76,0:13:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重皇及超重機組各機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.40,0:13:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將在135秒後進入\N與外星異種作戰的空域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.47,0:13:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來軍方打算無視我們的請求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.61,0:13:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.04,0:13:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.11,0:13:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管任何時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.05,0:13:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人心都是難以推測的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.27,0:14:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司，去引誘外星異種\N讓牠注意我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.47,0:14:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，讓妳瞧瞧我訓練的成果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.38,0:14:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.02,0:14:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去!糟糕了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.37,0:14:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司，你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.94,0:14:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是剛剛的那女孩在...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.44,0:14:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.38,0:14:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.58,0:14:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.82,0:14:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全超重機組\N進入合神領域了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.79,0:14:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G戰騎的諸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.89,0:14:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啟動合神吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.99,0:15:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工學型態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.79,0:15:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重合神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.45,0:16:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神機超重神合神完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.41,0:16:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫微洞崩壞加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.28,0:16:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各機組正常運作中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.18,0:16:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力子安定指數98%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.99,0:16:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.89,0:16:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次又會進化到什麼程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.30,0:16:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重破壞砲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.13,0:16:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有效...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.33,0:16:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每一發都被彈開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.35,0:17:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神機超重神被...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.98,0:17:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒下了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.65,0:17:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個外星異種有著令人難以置信\N的硬度與力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.66,0:17:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人似乎有增強裝甲的樣子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.13,0:17:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右腳飛彈發射口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.83,0:17:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及左上腕部連結部份受損
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.47,0:17:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力子安定供給迴路發生異常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.20,0:17:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副系統啟動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.37,0:17:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離臨界點為止5433點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.18,0:17:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左上腕部連結部份受損...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.38,0:17:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那豈不是無法發射\N超重壓力拳了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.88,0:17:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.25,0:17:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重壓力拳並不只一個喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.65,0:17:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.39,0:17:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦!該不會......
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.89,0:17:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右側重鑽機座艙\N超重壓力拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.39,0:17:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射預備!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.43,0:17:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要...要由我來發射嗎~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.91,0:17:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.61,0:18:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擊出!!壓力拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.14,0:18:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有效?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.90,0:18:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.77,0:18:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真...真的很對不起各位...\N都是我能力不夠......
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.74,0:18:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是妳的錯，愛娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.34,0:18:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙，只能使用劍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.65,0:18:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.82,0:18:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劍身亮現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.60,0:18:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工學終結!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.72,0:19:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧... 超重劍...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.29,0:19:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然也沒有效用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.49,0:19:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.29,0:19:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離臨界點為止1922點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.00,0:19:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙!用超重弧光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.13,0:19:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，\N只會讓臨界值更加接近而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.90,0:19:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.17,0:19:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這...這該怎麼辦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.57,0:19:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用超重新月鏢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.61,0:19:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.67,0:19:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是G戰影的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.71,0:19:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G戰影的翅膀是可以當作武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.95,0:19:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個女孩耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.65,0:19:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一位就是G戰影的飛行員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.15,0:19:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是第六位G戰騎成員，對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.72,0:19:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.96,0:19:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.89,0:20:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.33,0:20:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.90,0:20:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.10,0:20:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G戰影超重新月鏢\N發射預備!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.71,0:20:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重新月鏢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.44,0:20:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.47,0:20:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再向各位作一次介紹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.91,0:20:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G戰影的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.41,0:20:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.78,0:20:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.15,0:20:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裘伊露，早上也是得安靜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.52,0:20:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止為我們解危的\N就是妳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.33,0:21:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教，莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.90,0:21:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.15,0:21:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看著在烈陽熱氣下\N道路的那一方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.40,0:21:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,形形色色的事物\N呈現形形色色的擺動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.84,0:21:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知該為何這般\N心頭思緒紛亂不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.55,0:22:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但就這麼視而不見\N朝向明日飛去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.02,0:22:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為無法接受如此的不成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.19,0:22:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才說出了這麼不客氣的話語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.63,0:22:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若只是孤單一人地強出頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.47,0:22:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換來的只有誤解\N矛盾與迷惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.34,0:22:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於那牽繫著悲傷的羈絆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.61,0:22:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓微笑的雙眸中滲出了淚水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.08,0:22:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多想將這暖意傳送出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.85,0:22:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便緊握著手一直不願放開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.69,0:22:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好讓這祈禱得以傳達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.73,0:22:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜小姐，茶點跟便當都準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.87,0:22:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G戰騎的諸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.97,0:22:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向莉露的歡迎野餐會前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.77,0:22:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回播出"沒有笑容的少女"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.81,0:23:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下週也會照料各位的和平!